11:08.527 --> 11:12.831
You have a psychological
disorder called nyctophobia.

11:12.966 --> 11:14.333
It's a fear of the dark.

11:14.466 --> 11:16.335
It's a part of a
generalized anxiety disorder,

11:16.468 --> 11:20.706
and it is more common in
children, rarely in adults.

11:20.839 --> 11:23.275
Do you often have
heart palpitations

11:23.408 --> 11:26.345
and excessive sweating

11:26.478 --> 11:29.314
and... breathlessness?

11:29.448 --> 11:33.452
Maybe even... the
fear that you're dying?

11:33.585 --> 11:35.420
