11:35.554 --> 11:38.290
You are a highly decorated
FBI agent

11:38.423 --> 11:41.393
and you had a
full-blown anxiety attack.

11:41.526 --> 11:45.031
Have you had these
symptoms before?

11:45.163 --> 11:46.966
Who's this?

11:47.100 --> 11:48.266
That's my father.

11:48.400 --> 11:51.203
Answer the questions, Tony.

12:00.947 --> 12:04.783
We had something
similar at my mom's house.

12:04.916 --> 12:07.252
That was a long time ago.

12:09.821 --> 12:12.491
Okay, Tony.
It's your turn.

12:12.624 --> 12:15.594
Tell me the name and the
meaning of those flowers.

12:19.431 --> 12:21.733
Tony, what's wrong?

12:21.867 --> 12:23.201
Tony, don't be silent.

12:23.335 --> 12:26.039
Silence is a box
we need to open.

12:30.342 --> 12:32.744
Daisies.
It means loyal love.

12:32.878 --> 12:33.679
Yes.

12:33.812 --> 12:35.213
Mom, your name
should be Daisy.

12:43.156 --> 12:45.490
Whoa.

12:45.624 --> 12:47.693
I keep telling you,
I don't care...

12:47.826 --> 12:49.528
Mo... Mom?

12:49.661 --> 12:52.065
I didn't say that.
It's none of my business.

12:52.197 --> 12:53.632
Nothing to worry about.

12:53.765 --> 12:56.668
Don't ever show people
that you're afraid.

12:58.537 --> 13:01.974
Look, I have a little
trick when I feel scared.

13:02.108 --> 13:04.409
I whistle a nice melody
and my fears go away.

13:04.543 --> 13:05.777
