14:09.307 --> 14:12.011
nine...

14:12.145 --> 14:14.813
eight...

14:14.947 --> 14:17.749
seven...

14:17.883 --> 14:20.585
six...

14:20.719 --> 14:21.920
five...

14:22.054 --> 14:24.656
Don't hide under the
floor like you always do!

14:27.692 --> 14:29.394
