14:50.882 --> 14:52.417
Tony?

15:26.852 --> 15:29.621
- Hi.
- Good afternoon, ma'am.

15:29.754 --> 15:32.824
It's my car.
Such an old model.

15:32.959 --> 15:34.826
I think it ran out
of water again.

15:34.961 --> 15:36.628
I'm wondering if
you could help me out.

15:36.761 --> 15:37.896
Oh yeah, yeah, don't worry.

15:38.030 --> 15:39.531
I'll, uh... I'll
bring a container.

15:39.664 --> 15:41.067
- You can fill it with our hose.
- Thank you.

15:54.180 --> 15:57.549
