you don't tell me.

18:05.777 --> 18:07.545
No, no!

18:14.353 --> 18:16.188
What are you looking at?

18:17.655 --> 18:19.225
Stay here!

18:27.665 --> 18:29.601
Where... where are you?!

18:34.507 --> 18:36.541
No, no, no, no!

18:36.674 --> 18:37.977
No!

18:45.484 --> 18:48.020
Mama!
Mama, is that you?

18:49.388 --> 18:52.425
I stayed hidden
like a weakling

18:52.557 --> 18:54.393
