or something rotten.

19:01.866 --> 19:04.669
How long
were you in there?

19:04.803 --> 19:06.939
Three days.

19:26.658 --> 19:28.027
Let's get out of here.

19:32.932 --> 19:34.632
I was
sent back to Venezuela

19:34.766 --> 19:36.734
to be raised by my aunt.

19:38.736 --> 19:42.341
I couldn't stand being in
the dark for several years.

20:13.805 --> 20:17.076
