got over my fear.

20:20.812 --> 20:22.515
Until I saw the same man

20:22.647 --> 20:26.218
in... in the brothel that night.

20:26.352 --> 20:28.686
It happened again.

20:28.820 --> 20:30.788
Did they ever
find your sister?

20:36.328 --> 20:37.662
