You finally made it here.

26:29.882 --> 26:31.116
I apologize.

26:31.250 --> 26:33.185
Last night, I didn't know
that you were...

26:33.318 --> 26:34.954
well, I mean, that you are...

26:35.087 --> 26:36.655
