- You got it.

27:11.024 --> 27:12.558
It's nothing against you.

27:12.691 --> 27:15.627
I'm just allergic to bodyguards
walking in mute mode next to me.

27:15.761 --> 27:19.765
You won't even
notice that I'm around.

27:19.898 --> 27:21.433
Heh.

27:22.167 --> 27:24.037
I'll tell ya what.

27:24.169 --> 27:26.738
You keep your job by...

27:26.872 --> 27:31.777
walking my dog and getting me
things from the grocery store.

27:31.910 --> 27:34.346
Is that okay with you?

27:34.479 --> 27:35.914
Yeah.

27:36.049 --> 27:38.017
I'm thrilled by
my new assignment.

27:38.150 --> 27:40.285
What's the name of the puppy?

27:40.419 --> 27:42.588
Curvy. Would you
like to see a picture?

27:42.721 --> 27:43.789
Do I need to?

27:43.922 --> 27:46.258
They say dogs look
like their owners.

27:48.193 --> 27:50.195
I'll take that
as a compliment.

27:50.329 --> 27:51.965
Check it out for yourself.

27:54.733 --> 27:57.202
My Curvy is the next
best thing to an angel.

27:59.371 --> 28:01.373
Now that I know my new task,

28:01.506 --> 28:03.241
I think I better
go and wait outside.

28:03.375 --> 28:04.876
I'll escort you back home.

28:05.011 --> 28:06.812
You don't need
to wait outside.

28:06.946 --> 28:11.149
Here you go!
The two absolute finest

28:11.283 --> 28:14.087
New York egg creams
in the world.

28:14.219 --> 28:15.587
Thank you, darling.

28:15.721 --> 28:17.056
Enjoy.

28:23.428 --> 28:27.666
Sweetener.
Do you want some?

28:27.799 --> 28:29.368
No, thanks.

28:32.204 --> 28:34.107
