28:34.239 --> 28:35.108
Relax!

28:35.240 --> 28:37.242
Enjoy your drink.

28:37.376 --> 28:39.311
Have fun at work.

28:42.614 --> 28:44.883
Look at us, getting
to know each other.

28:45.018 --> 28:47.120
Establishing boundaries.

28:47.252 --> 28:50.355
Exchanging information.

28:50.489 --> 28:52.591
You get to know your employer.

28:54.493 --> 28:56.628
