29:05.737 --> 29:07.205
Uh, where are the napkins?

29:07.339 --> 29:10.208
Can you grab me a napkin
from that table, please?

29:20.218 --> 29:22.989
Don't forget that.

29:23.122 --> 29:24.456
Grab one.

29:24.589 --> 29:27.126
You seem to me like a man
who needs a bad habit.

29:36.468 --> 29:38.603
Cheers.

29:38.737 --> 29:40.472
This is on the house, honey.

29:40.605 --> 29:44.409
I felt negative vibes
with your angry boyfriend.

29:44.543 --> 29:46.946
He's a bodyguard.
He's not angry.

30:04.429 --> 30:09.234
It's
nothing personal.

30:09.367 --> 30:10.635
Just tell my husband that

30:10.769 --> 30:13.805
this is what I do to
his private detectives.

30:19.644 --> 30:22.215
I'll leave
you guys the check.

30:22.347 --> 30:23.950
No rush.

30:24.083 --> 30:25.917
Are you okay, Dennis?

30:26.052 --> 30:28.553
I'll take
care of it, honey.

30:37.029 --> 30:41.533
I told you... you
needed a bad habit.

31:34.386 --> 31:35.320
You like that?

31:37.223 --> 31:39.558
Stop! Stop, please!

31:39.691 --> 31:40.692
Do you want it again?
Do you?

31:42.327 --> 31:43.695
You want it again?

31:43.829 --> 31:45.097
Yeah! hit him!

31:52.904 --> 31:54.639
