31:54.773 --> 31:57.210
Please tell her
not to beat my boy!

32:10.056 --> 32:12.058
Oh.

32:12.191 --> 32:16.528
Long gone are the days when you
looked like a truck stop hooker!

32:16.661 --> 32:19.364
