33:16.022 --> 33:18.690
What do you want for her, huh?

33:18.823 --> 33:21.193
To be a loose bitch like you?

33:21.327 --> 33:25.463
You think
you're squared up, hm?

33:27.599 --> 33:30.102
You're still a bitch...

33:30.236 --> 33:31.636
