bones like crackers.

34:15.281 --> 34:17.248
Okay, where is she?

34:17.382 --> 34:19.516
Bring her now!

34:21.420 --> 34:23.554
Your sister was sick.

34:23.688 --> 34:25.590
Very sick.

34:25.724 --> 34:27.259
