34:27.393 --> 34:30.695
I swear to god, I'm going
to expose you to the police

34:30.829 --> 34:32.931
if you don't bring me Lana now.

34:37.370 --> 34:40.005
Here lies your sister, Lana.

34:40.139 --> 34:44.976
And I am making my
delivery as I promised.

34:46.643 --> 34:49.514
Archangels' trumpets shall blow

34:49.647 --> 34:52.817
