influences of the world.

35:06.898 --> 35:10.869
I am a man of my word.

35:11.003 --> 35:13.905
Take your sister with you.

35:17.776 --> 35:22.314
And keep bringing me
my money same as today.

35:22.448 --> 35:24.517
