surrounded by those mean people

38:04.310 --> 38:07.580
at that nasty place
they call The Atelier.

38:07.712 --> 38:09.548
It's not even a whorehouse.

38:09.682 --> 38:11.650
It's a living hell.

38:11.783 --> 38:13.285
Who's Lana?

38:13.419 --> 38:15.853
My sister.

38:15.988 --> 38:19.158
A hooker... just like me.

38:22.428 --> 38:27.199
- I hate Vincent!
- Just... calm down.

38:27.333 --> 38:31.803
Is that the man
who runs the place?

38:31.937 --> 38:33.871
I'm sure he did
something to her.

38:34.974 --> 38:37.343
Someday he'll come after me.

38:37.476 --> 38:39.345
You gotta stay strong.

38:39.478 --> 38:43.415
Rest assured nothing is gonna
happen to you, Mrs. Crawford.

38:43.549 --> 38:45.584
Rebecca!

38:45.718 --> 38:47.386
Rebecca is my real name.

38:47.519 --> 38:48.954
It's my only name!

38:51.457 --> 38:55.027
