40:30.422 --> 40:31.824
Look at this.

40:31.957 --> 40:33.492
Come here.

40:35.728 --> 40:37.363
This is so cool.

40:40.865 --> 40:42.101
What's in there?

40:55.447 --> 40:59.485
I want my toys!
