41:15.734 --> 41:17.770
It was driving me mad.

41:17.902 --> 41:19.872
I was like...

41:20.005 --> 41:23.442
how could this be
happening to me?

41:23.575 --> 41:24.943
I looked everywhere.

41:25.077 --> 41:27.346
I saw nothing.

41:29.581 --> 41:35.254
Then I lifted my butt up
and had a warm sensation.

41:38.524 --> 41:41.660
And I found it!

41:45.964 --> 41:48.434
When are you
gonna cure me, Daddy?

41:48.567 --> 41:50.502
Help.

41:57.576 --> 41:59.678
Shh. Shh.

42:04.049 --> 42:06.585
It's okay.
I'll get you another cat.

42:16.762 --> 42:18.397
She's harmless.

42:22.868 --> 42:25.939
My daughter's immune
system is attacking her.

42:26.071 --> 42:27.639
I brought you here
to entertain her.

42:27.773 --> 42:30.809
But first, I have to make
sure you're healthy girls.

42:30.944 --> 42:35.214
So I'm going to give you
a couple of health tests.

42:35.347 --> 42:37.983
I want you to wait in
the room next door.

42:38.116 --> 42:39.885
I feel okay.

42:40.018 --> 42:41.720
Please.

42:48.560 --> 42:51.597
Onacona, I'm gonna check you.

42:51.730 --> 42:53.365
So be a good girl.

42:57.035 --> 42:59.004
Foot up, please.

43:03.008 --> 43:04.543
Okay.

43:08.614 --> 43:09.815
Oh.

43:09.949 --> 43:11.683
It's normal to have all
the swelling and bruising.

43:11.817 --> 43:15.621
And the blood along
the stitches is normal.

43:15.754 --> 43:17.489
It's healing.

43:17.623 --> 43:20.325
And you're gonna
do a lot better.

43:20.459 --> 43:23.161
Those sweet young girls
that you just met,

43:23.295 --> 43:25.297
they're going to help us.

43:25.430 --> 43:30.135
They were kind enough to donate
their skin to your cause.

43:33.805 --> 43:36.775
And daddy will get you
another kitten, okay?

43:44.716 --> 43:48.053
Hey, do you wanna
get laid now or what?

43:48.186 --> 43:49.788
Don't grab me like that.

43:49.922 --> 43:51.623
Hey, stop!

43:51.757 --> 43:53.026
Get off of me!

43:53.158 --> 43:54.192
- Aah!
- THE CRADLE:

44:51.050 --> 44:53.819
I don't
expect any less from you.

45:41.067 --> 45:43.735
I'm here to guide you.

45:43.869 --> 45:47.773
My mission is to make sure that
both get to the Spirit World

45:47.906 --> 45:49.541
in a peaceful way.

45:53.445 --> 45:55.814
Sleep well.

45:55.948 --> 45:59.685
You'll be newborns again.

45:59.818 --> 46:01.520
I am your cradle.

48:24.896 --> 48:26.531
No! Stop!

48:28.667 --> 48:29.868
You shouldn't shout like that

48:30.002 --> 48:32.604
when someone's
near the edge of a cliff.

48:35.407 --> 48:37.709
Tony, are you afraid of dying?

48:37.843 --> 48:39.045
No.

48:41.280 --> 48:42.914
But I do my best to avoid it.

48:43.049 --> 48:46.418
You don't trust me.
I know that.

48:46.551 --> 48:49.721
Why don't we go
back to the car?

48:49.855 --> 48:51.290
You'll have to walk my dog

48:51.423 --> 48:54.426
and help me shop at the farmers'
market, I warned you.

49:15.914 --> 49:17.950
What happened to your neck?

49:20.886 --> 49:22.955
You mean the spots on my skin.

49:23.089 --> 49:26.758
Every week, there was a client
that used to visit Vincent.

49:26.892 --> 49:30.762
This man would pick
one of us at random.

49:33.531 --> 49:35.034
And one night, it was my turn.

49:35.167 --> 49:37.435
I let him put a needle in me,
thought it was dope.

49:37.569 --> 49:40.672
He ran out of it
and went to get more.

49:40.805 --> 49:43.842
I remember I saw
myself in the mirror.

49:43.976 --> 49:46.379
And I noticed...

49:46.511 --> 49:49.315
several bleached spots
on my skins.

49:49.447 --> 49:51.117
Where exactly is The Atelier?

49:52.285 --> 49:53.585
I want to meet that man

49:53.718 --> 49:56.055
and find out what really
happened to your sister.

49:56.188 --> 49:57.722
It's too late for that.

50:01.193 --> 50:02.995
You see, you don't know
what it feels like

50:03.129 --> 50:05.730
making a mistake
that you regret forever.

50:08.267 --> 50:09.768
When I was 12...

50:15.174 --> 50:19.078
...my mother...

50:19.211 --> 50:21.913
she was murdered.

50:22.048 --> 50:27.119
And my sister... she was
taken away because of me.

50:30.189 --> 50:34.559
I do know about regrets.

50:34.693 --> 50:37.229
It happened a long time ago.

50:37.363 --> 50:39.597
And I never saw her again.

50:39.731 --> 50:43.202
But I won't give up
until I find her,

50:43.336 --> 50:46.405
in this or the next life.

50:46.538 --> 50:48.074
Don't lose hope.

50:54.813 --> 50:57.083
I wish I had known you before.

50:58.184 --> 50:59.584
You shouldn't
whisper like that

50:59.718 --> 51:01.454
when someone is
near the edge of a cliff.

51:21.240 --> 51:24.076
If you think introducing
me to my wife was a favor,

51:24.210 --> 51:26.445
you're wrong.

51:26.578 --> 51:29.281
Get in here,
let's make this fast.

51:32.318 --> 51:35.421
This is the damn holy grail
we've been looking for.

51:35.553 --> 51:37.089
Hydroquinone.

51:37.223 --> 51:39.291
It's a bleaching drug.

51:39.425 --> 51:40.892
Harmless in small quantities,

51:41.027 --> 51:46.032
but deadly when
highly concentrated.

51:46.165 --> 51:49.301
I mean, the quantity that... that
monster needs to do something

51:49.435 --> 51:52.038
like this must be humongous.

51:52.171 --> 51:54.140
Look at her face.

51:54.273 --> 51:56.641
That's the real
color of her skin.

51:57.675 --> 51:59.178
That changed
back to normal.

51:59.311 --> 52:01.280
The effect was temporary,
but the damage is permanent.

52:01.414 --> 52:05.617
These... these black spots
popped up as a consequence.

52:07.486 --> 52:08.620
Look at this.

52:13.658 --> 52:18.630
See, this foam made us
think it was only the fentanyl.

52:18.763 --> 52:21.200
He drugs them
with the opioid

52:21.333 --> 52:23.902
and bleaches their skin
afterwards.

52:34.413 --> 52:36.348
We should
build a treehouse one day.

52:36.482 --> 52:37.816
That sounds great.

52:37.950 --> 52:40.752
We'll use these trunks
to slide from above.

52:40.885 --> 52:42.687
Do you think
this is a good idea?

52:42.821 --> 52:44.923
What?
Making a treehouse?

52:45.057 --> 52:46.992
No, what we came here for.

52:47.126 --> 52:48.593
Nothing bad is gonna happen.

52:48.726 --> 52:50.062
That's our escape route.

52:50.196 --> 52:54.467
Don't worry,
they won't follow us.

52:54.599 --> 52:56.102
Oh, wow, we better leave, Ana.

52:56.235 --> 52:58.070
We'll grab a piece
of honeycomb and flee.

52:58.204 --> 53:00.539
- Understood? Do it!
- Okay.

53:02.274 --> 53:03.675
- Come on, Tony, run!
- Ow!

53:03.808 --> 53:06.212
Move, Tony!
Move, move, Tony! Move!

53:08.314 --> 53:10.815
- Help me!
- Hold my hand!

53:10.950 --> 53:13.385
Hold my hand!

53:15.988 --> 53:20.392
Oh, she had rough, but
beautiful hands, Bobby.

53:26.565 --> 53:28.200
Thanks.

53:28.334 --> 53:30.402
Don't thank me.

53:30.536 --> 53:32.271
Just do your job.

53:35.241 --> 53:37.243
I could prepare
a bleaching cream using

53:37.376 --> 53:41.547
hydroquinone for
age spots, like this.

53:43.182 --> 53:44.483
As a matter of fact,
any experienced pharmacist

53:44.617 --> 53:45.951
could do it, Tony.

53:46.085 --> 53:47.987
But, pay attention.

53:48.120 --> 53:51.490
I wouldn't use more than
an 8% concentration level,

53:51.624 --> 53:54.193
which is enough to make you
look like Michael Jackson.

53:57.096 --> 53:59.331
Let me see what you
brought me this time.

54:24.323 --> 54:25.591
This is the highest
concentration

54:25.723 --> 54:27.359
I've seen in my life.

54:29.094 --> 54:31.796
If he was to use a
cream on somebody...

54:31.931 --> 54:34.400
- What if it's not a cream?
- What?

54:34.533 --> 54:37.403
What if it's
taken intravenously?

54:37.536 --> 54:39.171
Are you serious?

54:39.305 --> 54:42.840
It would be a death sentence.

54:42.975 --> 54:45.578
My supplier, a
pharmaceutical company,

54:45.710 --> 54:49.448
is the only place you can
buy it in big quantities.

54:49.582 --> 54:50.848
And they wouldn't sell it

54:50.983 --> 54:52.750
to just any John Doe
with a checkbook.

54:52.884 --> 54:54.420
- Linda?
- What?

54:54.553 --> 54:57.289
Could you please get me a
list of all their customers?

54:57.423 --> 55:00.192
I don't know if I can.

55:00.326 --> 55:02.760
- I... I would have to check.
- I need it.

55:02.894 --> 55:04.063
Please, you have to.

55:04.196 --> 55:07.600
- I'll do what I can...
- Hold on.

55:07.732 --> 55:09.668
Where are you heading now?

55:10.735 --> 55:12.071
Damn it!

55:29.555 --> 55:31.323
Wake up, Vincent.

55:47.306 --> 55:51.577
I guess you rich people don't
let your debts go delinquent,

55:51.710 --> 55:53.145
do you?

55:54.313 --> 55:57.915
By the way,
I'm sorry about the other day.

56:02.621 --> 56:04.889
